description: The family flew back from Greece after just a day on holiday there, amid intense criticism.
title: Coronavirus: Dutch royals return amid anger over Covid holiday
title_page: Coronavirus: Dutch royals return amid anger over Covid holiday - BBC News
maintext: The royal statement read: "We do not want to leave any doubts about it: in order to get the Covid-19 virus under control, it is necessary that the guidelines are followed. The debate over our holiday does not contribute to that."
